🛒 Blinkit Sales Dashboard | Power BI Project

📌 Overview
An interactive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze Blinkit’s sales data and uncover meaningful business insights. This project demonstrates how raw data can be transformed into clear, actionable intelligence through effective visualization.

🎯 Purpose
Build hands-on experience with real-world data analysis
Strengthen Power BI, DAX, and data storytelling skills
Showcase ability to create business-focused dashboards

🛠️ Tech Stack
Power BI (Data Visualization)
Power Query (Data Cleaning & Transformation)
DAX (KPIs & Calculations)
Dataset (Sales & Product Data)

📊 Dashboard Highlights
📈 Sales performance tracking
🛍️ Product category analysis
🌍 Outlet/location-wise insights
⭐ Customer ratings & behavior
💰 Key KPIs (Revenue, Avg Sales, Trends)

🔍 Key Insights
Identified top-performing products and categories
Discovered sales trends and customer preferences
Highlighted underperforming areas for improvement

🚀 What This Project Shows

✔ Data cleaning & transformation skills
✔ Strong understanding of business metrics
✔ Ability to design interactive dashboards
✔ Clear and effective data storytelling

